R", "words": [15, 16, 17]}, {"id": 4, "text": "ED Choisissez la bonne réponse.", "words": [18, 19, 20, 21, 22]}, {"id": 5, "text": "1.", "words": [23]}, {"id": 6, "text": "Vous payez comment ?", "words": [24, 25, 26, 27]}, {"id": 7, "text": "a.", "words": [28]}, {"id": 8, "text": "Avec mon porte-monnaie.", "words": [29, 30, 31]}, {"id": 9, "text": "b.", "words": [32]}, {"id": 10, "text": "Par chèque.", "words": [33, 34]}, {"id": 11, "text": "2.", "words": [35]}, {"id": 12, "text": "Vous avez la monnaie ?", "words": [36, 37, 38, 39, 40]}, {"id": 13, "text": "a.", "words": [41]}, {"id": 14, "text": "Non, je n'ai pas d'argent.", "words": [42, 43, 44, 45, 46]}, {"id": 15, "text": "b.", "words": [47]}, {"id": 16, "text": "Non, j'ai seulement un billet de 20 €.", "words": [48, 49, 50, 51, 52, 53, 54, 55]}, {"id": 17, "text": "3.", "words": [56]}, {"id": 18, "text": "Il me faut de la monnaie pour prendre un chariot au supermarché.", "words": [57, 58, 59, 60, 61, 62, 63, 64, 65, 66, 67, 68]}, {"id": 19, "text": "a.", "words": [69]}, {"id": 20, "text": "Tiens, voilà une pièce de 1 €.", "words": [70, 71, 72, 73, 74, 75, 76]}, {"id": 21, "text": "b.", "words": [77]}, {"id": 22, "text": "Tiens, voilà un billet de 50 €.", "words": [78, 79, 80, 81, 82, 83, 84]}, {"id": 23, "text": "4.", "words": [85]}, {"id": 24, "text": "Vous avez l'appoint ?", "words": [86, 87, 88, 89]}, {"id": 25, "text": "a.", "words": [90]}, {"id": 26, "text": "| _|Oui, voilà 8,95 €.", "words": [91, 92, 93, 94, 95]}, {"id": 27, "text": "b.", "words": [96]}, {"id": 28, "text": "|__| Oui, voilà de l'argent.", "words": [97, 98, 99, 100, 101]}, {"id": 29, "text": "5.", "words": [102]}, {"id": 30, "text": "Le chèque est à quel ordre ?", "words": [103, 104, 105, 106, 107, 108, 109]}, {"id": 31, "text": "a.", "words": [110]}, {"id": 32, "text": "91,68 euros.", "words": [111, 112]}, {"id": 33, "text": "b.", "words": [113]}, {"id": 34, "text": "[] Grégoire Lambert.", "words": [114, 115, 116]}, {"id": 35, "text": "6.", "words": [117]}, {"id": 36, "text": "Que fait la vendeuse ?", "words": [118, 119, 120, 121, 122]}, {"id": 37, "text": "a.", "words": [123]}, {"id": 38, "text": "|__| Elle me rend mon argent.", "words": [124, 125, 126, 127, 128, 129]}, {"id": 39, "text": "b.", "words": [130]}, {"id": 40, "text": "me rend la monnaie.", "words": [131, 132, 133, 134]}, {"id": 41, "text": "7.", "words": [135]}, {"id": 42, "text": "Sabine a de l'argent ?", "words": [136, 137, 138, 139, 140]}, {"id": 43, "text": "a.", "words": [141]}, {"id": 44, "text": "Non, elle n'a pas de monnaie.", "words": [142, 143, 144, 145, 146, 147]}, {"id": 45, "text": "b.", "words": [148]}, {"id": 46, "text": "Oui, mais elle n'a pas de monnaie.", "words": [149, 150, 151, 152, 153, 154, 155]}, {"id": 47, "text": "EP Vrai ou faux ?", "words": [156, 157, 158, 159, 160]}, {"id": 48, "text": "VRAI FAUX 1.", "words": [161, 162, 163]}, {"id": 49, "text": "Si vous avez l'appoint, le commerçant vous rend la monnaie.", "words": [164, 165, 166, 167, 168, 169, 170, 171, 172, 173]}, {"id": 50, "text": "2.", "words": [174]}, {"id": 51, "text": "On met les pièces dans un portefeuille.", "words": [175, 176, 177, 178, 179, 180, 181]}, {"id": 52, "text": "3.", "words": [182]}, {"id": 53, "text": "Si vous ne payez pas en liquide, vous pouvez payer en espèces.", "words": [183, 184, 185, 186, 187, 188, 189, 190, 191, 192, 193, 194]}, {"id": 54, "text": "4.", "words": [195]}, {"id": 55, "text": "Nous pouvons faire un chèque à un médecin.", "words": [196, 197, 198, 199, 200, 201, 202, 203]}, {"id": 56, "text": "5.", "words": [204]}, {"id": 57, "text": "Si vous achetez une baguette avec un billet de 50 €, on vous rendra la monnaie.", "words": [205, 206, 207, 208, 209, 210, 211, 212, 213, 214, 215, 216, 217, 218, 219, 220]}, {"id": 58, "text": "6.", "words": [221]}, {"id": 59, "text": "On doit signer un chéquier après l'avoir rempli.", "words": [222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227, 228, 229]}, {"id": 60, "text": "7.", "words": [230]}, {"id":